---
title: Crispy Chicken Milanese with Roasted Summer Squash, Tomatoes, and Arugula
description: Panko breadcrumbs and sour cream are the secret to this crispy chicken Milanese. For a light, yet hearty meal, we’re serving it alongside sweet roasted squash and a bright side salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/594ab8ba4f78db1340108342-54870762.jpg
